snippet.title: Night at the Gates of Hell - Official Trailer | The Indie Horror Showcase 2023
snippet.description: Check out the trailer for Night at the Gates of Hell. From the sick mind behind Bloodwash, Jordan King, comes his latest experiment in terror. Inspired by the Italian zombie flicks from Lucio Fulci and Bruno Mattei, Night of the Gates of Hell promises to be a blood dripping, neon soaked, flesh rotting experience. Out now on PlayStation, Nintendo Switch, and Steam.
